graphql.query:
mutation {
    addEmployee(
        first_name: "Eric",
        last_name: "L",
        email: "ericL@mail.com",
        gender: "Male",
        designation: "Developer",
        salary: 80000.0,
        date_of_joining: "2026-02-22",
        department: "IT",
        employee_photo: "data:image/jpeg;base64,"
  ) {
    id
    first_name
    last_name
  }
}

mutation AddEmployee($photo: String!) {
  addEmployee(
    
    first_name: "Eric",
    last_name: "Laudrum",
    email: "eric.laudrum@georgebrown.ca",
    gender: "Male",
    designation: "Software Developer",
    salary: 5000,
    date_of_joining: "2026-01-01",
    department: "IT",
    employee_photo: $photo
  ) {
    id
    first_name
    employee_photo
  }
}
